    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Argand lamps without a separate reservoir and with burners that have low dome deflectors with circular openings.  The font, if not the entire lamp, is made of metal, commonly brass.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
